Go to your master file

git branch
git branch friday-slides   ****creating your branch****
git checkout friday-slides   ****go to your branch****
git branch    ****check to see that you're on the right branch****

****alter your branch****
****commit changes****

git add -A
git commit -am""

****merge and push to repo****

git checkout master
git branch
git merge friday-slides
git add -A
git commit -am""
git push